title: Alonzo Williams: Eazy E Didn't Die of AIDS, He Was Murdered!
itunes:title: Alonzo Williams: Eazy E Didn't Die of AIDS, He Was Murdered!
description:
We sit down with legendary Compton music executive Alonzo Williams and he talks about discovering Dr. Dre and Michele', hooking NWA up with Jerry Heller and drops a bombshell about the late Eazy-E's death.
